Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:03.78,Pony,,0,0,0,,甜蜜日常 但仍有点混乱\N♪ It's a sweet life, still a little messy. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:05.74,Pony,,0,0,0,,奇妙日常 充满了惊喜\N♪ Magic life, full of surprises. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:06.69,Pony,,0,0,0,,迅捷日常\N♪ Fast life ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.79,RR,,0,0,0,,凝视我的宝石\N♪ Gaze upon my gems! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.49,Pony,,0,0,0,,开心日常 因为我们拥有彼此\N♪ It's a fun life because we got each other. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:13.49,Pony,,0,0,0,,可爱日常\N♪ It's a cute life. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.54,Pony,,0,0,0,,以自己的方式生活！\N♪ Living life in our own way! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.21,Pony,,0,0,0,,来吧 拿一块蛋糕\N♪ Come on, grab a slice of cake. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:20.19,Chorus,,0,0,0,,甜蜜 奇妙 迅捷 时尚 开心 可爱\N ♪ It's a sweet, magic, fast, posh, fun, cute ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:21.29,Pony,,0,0,0,,小马日常\N♪ Pony Life! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:23.17,Pony,,0,0,0,,每口都是甜蜜的惊喜\N♪ A sweet surprise in every bite.  ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.96,Pony,,0,0,0,,友谊 彩虹 真的棒\N♪ Friendship, rainbows, wuh-oh! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:25.55,FS,,0,0,0,,甜蜜\N♪ It's a sweet  ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.13,TS,,0,0,0,,奇妙\N♪ Magic ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:26.67,RD,,0,0,0,,迅捷\N♪ Fast ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:27.22,RR,,0,0,0,,时尚\N♪ Posh ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:27.72,AJ,,0,0,0,,开心\N♪ Fun ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:28.17,PP,,0,0,0,,可爱\N♪ Cut ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:31.03,Pony,,0,0,0,,小马日常\N♪ Pony Life! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:34.81,WISH,,0,0,0,,{\pos(522,378)\\frz29.58}最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.81,WISH,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1330,284)\frz31.76}愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:41.46,Pony,,0,0,0,,这种疯狂必须停止！\NThis madness has got to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:43.58,Pony,,0,0,0,,但是 只有许愿魔法\NBut wish magic is the only thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.62,Pony,,0,0,0,,强大到足以解除小马镇所有的混乱魔法\NPowerful enough to undo all the chaos magic in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.47,Pony,,0,0,0,,但无序拿走了所有的愿望！\NBut Discord took all the wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:51.02,Pony,,0,0,0,,等一下\NWait just a sugar-frosted second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.90,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们探索无序脑袋时\NWhile we were exploring Discord's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.56,Pony,,0,0,0,,我得知今天是他的生日\NI learned that today is his birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:57.52,Pony,,0,0,0,,事实上 他从来没有办过生日派对！\NIn fact, he's never had a birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,这意味着...\NWhich means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:00.65,Pony,,0,0,0,,他才一岁大！\NHe's one year old!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:02.87,Pony,,0,0,0,,不对 但我喜欢你的热情\NNo, but love the enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.75,Pony,,0,0,0,,这意味着 无序会得到一个生日愿望！\NIt means Discord gets a birthday wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:06.91,Pony,,0,0,0,,就这样！\NThat's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:09.83,Pony,,0,0,0,,让我们为无序举办一个最棒的生日派对吧！\NLet's throw Discord the best birthday party ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.47,Pony,,0,0,0,,这样 他会用他的生日愿望\NSo he'll use his birthday wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:14.51,Pony,,0,0,0,,让小马镇恢复正常！\Nto return Ponyville back to pony-normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.69,Pony,,0,0,0,,耶！但我们必须让它成为一个惊喜\NYes! Buuuut we gotta make it a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:20.75,Pony,,0,0,0,,以我对无序的了解\NKnowing Discord,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:22.19,Pony,,0,0,0,,他会像往常一样制造混乱\Nhe'd do his usual chaos thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.86,Pony,,0,0,0,,毁掉派对和我们最后的希望\Nand ruin the party and our last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:25.94,Pony,,0,0,0,,事情多 时间少！\NMuch to do and little time to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:28.22,Pony,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞和暮光 你们负责装饰\NRarity and Twilight, you're on decoration duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.32,Pony,,0,0,0,,阿杰和小蝶 你们负责音乐\NApplejack and Fluttershy, you take care of the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.22,Pony,,0,0,0,,我会烤出最酷的生日蛋糕\NI'll bake the coolest birthday cake ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:36.67,Pony,,0,0,0,,由我信任的副厨云宝黛茜协助\Naided by my trusted sous chef Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.62,Pony,,0,0,0,,你好 哈喽！\NHello and hellooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:42.92,Pony,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临“我们来装饰”\NWelcome to Let's Decorate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:44.80,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们让每个派对都精彩！\NWe make every party great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:47.25,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们需要一些紧急装饰品\NWe need some emergency decorations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:49.79,Pony,,0,0,0,,为了一个惊喜生日派对\Nfor a surprise birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:52.02,Pony,,0,0,0,,我爱惊喜！\NI love surprises!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.84,Pony,,0,0,0,,别告诉我是为谁准备的！\NDon't tell me who it's for!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.90,Pony,,0,0,0,,我想被惊喜到！\NI want to be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.10,Pony,,0,0,0,,是啊{\fs50}···\N{\fs70}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.25,Pony,,0,0,0,,所以我们需要横幅 气球 彩纸{\fs50}···\N{\fs70}So we're gonna need streamers, balloons, confetti...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.01,Pony,,0,0,0,,就把你们最好的东西都给我们吧\NJust give us all the best stuff you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.43,Pony,,0,0,0,,可我们就有最好的东西！\NBut we have the best stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.33,Pony,,0,0,0,,让我先看一眼我的储藏室\NLet me just peek into my storage room for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:10.22,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们什么都没有了\NWe're completely out of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:12.47,Pony,,0,0,0,,惊喜！\NSurprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:15.20,Pony,,0,0,0,,但你说你什么都有！\NBut you said you have all the things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.14,Pony,,0,0,0,,有啊！\NWe do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:17.18,Pony,,0,0,0,,但现在没有\NBut not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:20.16,Pony,,0,0,0,,整个店都租出去了 我一定是忘了\NThe whole store's been rented, and I must've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.62,Pony,,0,0,0,,是不是很傻？\NIsn't that silly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.12,Pony,,0,0,0,,最傻了\NThe silliest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.18,Pony,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办？我们需要装饰品\NWhat now? We need decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.50,Pony,,0,0,0,,暮光 亲爱的\NTwilight, darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.71,Pony,,0,0,0,,我可能正好有个解决办法\NI might just have a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:35.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰你 DJ Pon-3\NSorry to bother you, DJ Pon-3,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.18,Pony,,0,0,0,,但我们真的需要你的帮助\Nbut we really need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:38.35,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们要办派对\NWe're throwin' a party,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.42,Pony,,0,0,0,,想让它超级热闹\Nand we want to be a real barn-blaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.48,Pony,,0,0,0,,你能提供音乐吗？\NWill you provide the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.33,Pony,,0,0,0,,DJ Pon-3的电报\NTelegram for DJ Pon-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.40,Pony,,0,0,0,,恭喜\NCongrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.86,Pony,,0,0,0,,你赢得了为期两周的“阿斑马”热带绿洲度假\NYou won a two-week vacation to the tropical oasis of Azebra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.82,Pony,,0,0,0,,它马上开始 旅途愉快\NIt starts immediately. Happy travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.28,Pony,,0,0,0,,真倒霉\NTalk about bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:01.55,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们现在怎么办？\NWhat do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:04.16,Pony,,0,0,0,,呃  DJ Pon-3应该不介意\NUh, DJ Pon-3 doesn't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.62,Pony,,0,0,0,,小马租用她的设备 对吧？\Nwhen ponies rent her equipment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.63,Pony,,0,0,0,,我有个桶 里面装着些旧道具\NI have a bucket full of old props somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.64,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们可以把它们当装饰用\NWe can use them as decor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.01,Pony,,0,0,0,,在这儿！\NHere it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.76,Pony,,0,0,0,,棒极了\NWonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:21.92,Pony,,0,0,0,,可以吃吗？\NCan we eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:22.93,Pony,,0,0,0,,它看起来太棒了\NIt looks incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.52,Pony,,0,0,0,,我得吃了它！\NI need to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.68,Pony,,0,0,0,,还不行\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.40,Pony,,0,0,0,,先得涂糖霜\NFirst, we frost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.46,Pony,,0,0,0,,DJ Pon-3在哪？\NWhere's DJ Pon-3?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.82,Pony,,0,0,0,,没时间解释了！\NNo time for a recap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.40,Pony,,0,0,0,,无序三十分钟后在这儿见我\NDiscord's meeting me here in thirty minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.36,Pony,,0,0,0,,还有很多事要做！\Nand there's much to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.20,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们来装饰吧！\NLet's decorate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.98,Pony,,0,0,0,,《彭普兰斯的海盗》的道具\NProps from The Pirates of Penprance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,《侏罗纪马园》的恐龙装备\Ndino gear from Jurassic Horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:53.08,Pony,,0,0,0,,还有《独立草》里的外星人！\N...and the aliens from Independence Hay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,派对可能还有救！\NThe party just might be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.56,Pony,,0,0,0,,我的普通糖被换成了\NMy regular sugar was swapped
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.64,Pony,,0,0,0,,我特制的爆炸糖？\Nwith my special stash of exploding sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:13.07,Pony,,0,0,0,,不———！\NNoooooooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:14.86,Pony,,0,0,0,,咋了?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.95,Pony,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 这是你的生日\NHey, hey, it's your birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.16,Pony,,0,0,0,,欢呼 欢呼 又来到这一年\NCheer, cheer for another year
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.96,Pony,,0,0,0,,为你的特别日子欢呼！\NHooray for your special day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.20,Pony,,0,0,0,,多么混乱的景象啊！\NWhat a positively chaotic sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.21,Pony,,0,0,0,,让我猜猜\NLet me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,你们想让我的生日愿望\NYou want my birthday wish
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.60,Pony,,0,0,0,,把小马镇变回正常\Nto set Ponyville back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.22,Pony,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？\NHow did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:44.06,Pony,,0,0,0,,我无意中听到了你们的计划\NI overheard you ponies planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.35,Pony,,0,0,0,,我租了所有东西\NI rented everything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:48.27,Pony,,0,0,0,,从那家烦人又喜庆的小马装饰店\Nfrom that annoying cheerful decoration store pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:52.23,Pony,,0,0,0,,是我让DJ甩下你不管的\NI got the DJ to leave you in the lurch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.02,Pony,,0,0,0,,关于交换糖分？\NAnd swapping the sugars？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.95,Pony,,0,0,0,,我好奇那会发生什么\NI wonder how that could've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.21,Pony,,0,0,0,,惊喜！\NSurprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.36,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们早该知道\NWe should have known
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.95,Pony,,0,0,0,,这些疯狂不可能是巧合\Nthis craziness couldn't have been a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:04.50,Pony,,0,0,0,,我就是喜欢混乱！\NI just adore chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.99,Pony,,0,0,0,,我想 再见吧 生日愿望\NI suppose it's so long, birthday wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.29,Pony,,0,0,0,,再见吧 小马镇\Nand so long, Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.18,Pony,,0,0,0,,哦 你大错特错了！腐果卡壳\NOh, how wrong you are, "Frappleclack".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:14.27,Pony,,0,0,0,,毁掉的派对才是完美的派对！\NA ruined party is a perfect party!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:18.39,Pony,,0,0,0,,今天的混乱就是最棒的生日礼物\NToday's chaos has been the perfect birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:22.73,Pony,,0,0,0,,我会用我的生日愿望让小马镇恢复正常\NI'll use my birthday wish to return Ponyville to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.35,Pony,,0,0,0,,最好快点\NBetter do it quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.77,Pony,,0,0,0,,因为你的蜡烛快熄灭了！\N'cause your candle is almost out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:27.93,Pony,,0,0,0,,然后就再见了 愿望\NThen it'll be goodbye, wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:35.06,Pony,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC5FF1F&\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&HC62DF3&\fs110\xshad-2}不羁的心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.52,Pony,,0,0,0,,结{\fs50}···{\fs70}结束了？\NI-Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.30,Pony,,0,0,0,,咱{\fs50}···{\fs70}咱能看了吗？\NC-Can we look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.06,Pony,,0,0,0,,我认为它奏效了！\NI think it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.42,Pony,,0,0,0,,无序的愿望恢复了秩序！\NDiscord's wish has restored order!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.20,Pony,,0,0,0,,暮光？穗龙？\NTwilight? Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.45,Pony,,0,0,0,,哇哦！“暮光穗龙”！\NWhoa! "Twilight Spikle"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.78,Pony,,0,0,0,,哈哈  真好笑\NHa-ha, very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,等等 为什么我是穗龙？\NWait. Why am I Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,这太诡异了\NThis is freaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:04.14,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们的传送门出了点问题\NSomething's wrong with our portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.76,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们被直接吸回来了\NWe got sucked right back through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:07.93,Pony,,0,0,0,,感觉像是我们{\fs50}···{\fs70}\NIt's like we got...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.65,Pony,,0,0,0,,断开了连接\Ndisconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.39,Pony,,0,0,0,,有点不对劲\NSomethin's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.53,Pony,,0,0,0,,嗯  这是肯定的！\NWell, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:15.07,Pony,,0,0,0,,无序的生日愿望本该让一切恢复正常\NDiscord's birthday wish should've put everything back to normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.41,Pony,,0,0,0,,但现在反而比以前更混乱了！\Nbut everything is even more chaotic than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.53,Pony,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我得离开一会儿 接个电话\NSorry. Have to split for a moment and take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.70,Pony,,0,0,0,,哦 好吧 然后我说{\fs50}···{\fs70}\NOh, okay. And then I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.70,Pony,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以再试试——！\NMaybe we can try agaaaaain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.21,Pony,,0,0,0,,好听\NBravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.96,Pony,,0,0,0,,我在穗龙的身体里\NI'm in Spike's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.17,Pony,,0,0,0,,小蝶把每句话都唱出来\NFluttershy is singing everything she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.56,Pony,,0,0,0,,萍琪刚才接了个水果电话\NPinkie just answered a piece of fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.75,Pony,,0,0,0,,我认为\NI think
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.67,Pony,,0,0,0,,宇宙愿望能量和狂野魔法的混合\Nthat the mix of cosmic wish energy and the Wild Side magic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.24,Pony,,0,0,0,, 正在扰乱小马利亚的自然秩序！\Nis messing with the natural order of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:47.09,Pony,,0,0,0,,所以 无序的愿望不够强？\NSo Discord's wish wasn't strong enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.25,Pony,,0,0,0,,恐怕是的\NI'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:51.27,Pony,,0,0,0,,这就意味着 我们两个世界正在融合成一个！\NWhich means our two worlds are merging into one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.48,Pony,,0,0,0,,如果那样的话\NIf that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:55.27,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们要担心的就不止是一点点混乱了！\Nwe'll have more than a little chaos to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:58.52,Pony,,0,0,0,,这看起来不太妙——\NThis doesn't look goooooood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.78,Pony,,0,0,0,,冷静点 各位小马\NChill out, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,我想我们能清理掉这些散逸的狂野魔法\NI think we can clean up the loose Wild Side magic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.20,Pony,,0,0,0,,并让一切恢复正常\Nand set everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.58,Pony,,0,0,0,,而且我知道该怎么做\NAnd I know just how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.98,Pony,,0,0,0,,她很擅长清理 尤其是亮粉\NShe's very good at cleaning. Especially glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.65,Pony,,0,0,0,,还有 我储藏室里还放着那些奇怪的魔法物品\NAlso, I still have all those weird magical items in the pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.24,Pony,,0,0,0,,抱歉 妈妈 我待会再打给你\NSorry, mom. Gonna have to call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.36,Pony,,0,0,0,,得去拯救小马利亚了！\NGotta go save Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.01,Pony,,0,0,0,,好的 计划是什么？\NOkay! What's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:28.09,Pony,,0,0,0,,首先 我们需要那些物品\NFirst, we'll need those objects
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.01,Pony,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能为它们注入我们的魔法\Nso we can infuse them with our magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.78,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们得快点——！\NWe gotta hurryyyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.86,Pony,,0,0,0,,酷~\NCoooool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.24,Pony,,0,0,0,,让我们来试试它们吧！\NLet's test them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,现在它是一根传送门魔杖了\NNow it's a portal wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.92,AJ,,0,0,0,,前方的道路充满未知\N♪ The road ahead's uncertain ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.17,AJ,,0,0,0,,我们该走向何方\N♪ Which way will we go ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.51,AJ,,0,0,0,,才能收拾这魔法混乱？\N♪ To clean up this magic mass? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.26,AJ,,0,0,0,,哦 我们该如何知晓？\N♪ Oh, how will we know? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.19,FS,,0,0,0,,没有简单的指南\N♪ There is no simple guide ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.15,FS,,0,0,0,,没有地图指引方向\N♪ No map to lead the way ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.43,LC,,0,0,0,,只需倾听你狂野的心\N♪ Just listen to your wild heart ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.17,LC,,0,0,0,,听听它在说什么\N♪ And what it has to say ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.18,Chorus,,0,0,0,,上变下或下变上\N♪ Downside-up or upside-down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.69,Chorus,,0,0,0,,这个世界一片混乱\N♪ It's topsy-turvy all around ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.57,Chorus,,0,0,0,,只需去绽放你的光芒\N♪ Just go and shine your light ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:23.47,Chorus,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来\N♪ And it'll be all right ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.45,Chorus,,0,0,0,,上变下或下变上\N♪ Downside-up or upside-down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.77,Chorus,,0,0,0,,这个小镇一片混乱\N♪ It's topsy-turvy in the town ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.85,Chorus,,0,0,0,,不要放弃战斗\N♪ Don't give up the fight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.57,Chorus,,0,0,0,,朋友会让一切变好\N♪ Friends will make it right ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.45,TS,,0,0,0,,当一切都变得一团糟\N♪ When everything goes sideways ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.67,TS,,0,0,0,,我也总能依靠你\N♪ I can always count on you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.83,PP,,0,0,0,,当我的生活变得疯狂\N♪ When my life feels wacky ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.08,PP,,0,0,0,,你助我坚持下去\N♪ You help me to push through ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.96,AJ,,0,0,0,,变化有时让人觉得\N♪ Changing can sometimes feel like ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.04,AJ,,0,0,0,,世界就要终结\N♪ The world is gonna end ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.38,RD,,0,0,0,,但如果你学会顺应它\N♪ But if you learn to roll with it ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.01,Chorus,,0,0,0,,它能成为你朋友\N♪ It can be your friend! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.89,Pony,,0,0,0,,DJ Pon-3 来点超赞的节奏\NDJ Pon-3, bring that sweet, sweet beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.09,Chorus,,0,0,0,,{\an8}狂野之心！心跳不息！\N♪ Wild heart! Heart beats! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.56,Chorus,,0,0,0,,{\an8}狂野之心！心跳不息！\N♪ Wild heart! Heart beats! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.94,PP,,0,0,0,,去完未来又回来\N♪ Been to the future and back ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.02,PP,,0,0,0,,见过怪物植物攻击\N♪ Seen a monster plant attack ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.10,PP,,0,0,0,,玩过传送门战斗\N♪ Played some Portal Combat ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.14,PP,,0,0,0,,甚至遇到一只酷蝙蝠\N♪ Even met a cool bat ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.06,PP,,0,0,0,,戳破过巨大气球\N♪ Popped a giant balloon ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.02,PP,,0,0,0,,也见过机械小马\N♪ Met mechani-ponies, too ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.19,PP,,0,0,0,,弄了个闪亮发型\N♪ Got a sparkly updo ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.19,PP,,0,0,0,,遇到点彗星小麻烦\N♪ Had a little comet trouble ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.28,PP,,0,0,0,,被困在泡泡里面\N♪ Got caught in a bubble ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.74,PP,,0,0,0,,现在我们迷失在废墟\N♪ Now we're lost in the rubble ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.50,PP,,0,0,0,,但现在很清楚一点小混乱\N♪ But now it's clear to see a little chaos ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.76,PP,,0,0,0,,在和谐中有重要地位\N♪ Has a vital place in harmony ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.26,PP,,0,0,0,,没错 狂野是我的一部分\N♪ And yeah, wild is a part of me ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.03,Chorus,,0,0,0,,上变下或下变上\N♪ Downside-up or upside-down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.79,Chorus,,0,0,0,,这个世界一片混乱\N♪ It's topsy-turvy all around ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.40,Chorus,,0,0,0,,只需去绽放你的光芒\N♪ Just go and shine your light ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.42,Chorus,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来\N♪ And it'll be all right ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.36,Chorus,,0,0,0,,上变下或下变上\N♪ Downside-up or upside-down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.64,Chorus,,0,0,0,,这个小镇一片混乱\N♪ It's topsy-turvy in this town ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.80,Chorus,,0,0,0,,不要放弃战斗\N♪ Don't give up the fight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.72,Chorus,,0,0,0,,朋友会让一切变好\N♪ Friends will make it right ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:32.74,Chorus,,0,0,0,,不要放弃战斗\N♪ Don't give up the fight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.05,Chorus,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要放弃战斗\N♪ Don't give up the fight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.26,Chorus,,0,0,0,,不  别放弃战斗\N♪ No, don't give up the fight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.41,Chorus,,0,0,0,,朋友会让一切变好！\N♪ Friends will make it right! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.19,Pony,,0,0,0,,好了 小马们\NAll right, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:45.16,Pony,,0,0,0,,是时候彻底结束这场混乱了！\NIt's time to end this chaos once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.22,Pony,,0,0,0,,等等\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.69,Pony,,0,0,0,,这是不是意味着{\fs50}···{\fs70}\NDoes this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:48.94,Pony,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}···{\fs70}永别?\N...goodbye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.78,Pony,,0,0,0,,我想有可能\NI think it might.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.36,Pony,,0,0,0,,但这段时间很开心\NBut it's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,超级开心\NSuper fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.23,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们还会再见面的\NWe could meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:59.16,Pony,,0,0,0,,毕竟 你永远不知道未来会发生什么\NAfter all, you never know what the future holds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.93,Pony,,0,0,0,,嘿！我又变回我了！\NHey! I'm me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.10,Pony,,0,0,0,,{\an8}小马日常\N♪ Pony Life ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.31,Pony,,0,0,0,,{\an8}小马日常\N♪ Pony Life ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.31,Pony,,0,0,0,,{\an8}小马日常\N♪ Pony Life ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:26.68,Pony,,0,0,0,,以防这些小马们还需要一点点混乱\NJust in case these ponies are in need of a little more chaos.
